  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Multi-Tool</span>. This specialized tool comes with several <span class=\"name name-technology\">scanning</span> upgrades pre-installed, to increase the efficiency and profitability of scanning planetary discoveries.<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">Take</span> this Multi-Tool to add it to your collection, or <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exchange</span> it with your current Multi-Tool. Swap between active Multi-Tools from the Utilities section of the Quick Menu (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>).",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一台专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">多用途工具</span>。这件专门工具预装有多个<span class=\"name name-technology\">扫描</span>升级部件，能够有效提高扫描星球发现物的效率与收益。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">收下</span>这个多用途工具，将它加入你的收藏，或与你现在的多用途工具<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交换</span>。在快捷菜单（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）中的工具部分切换可用的多用途工具。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一個特殊<span class=\"name name-stellar\">工具組</span>。這個特殊的工具預裝了數個<span class=\"name name-technology\">掃描</span>升級，能增加掃描星球發現物的效率與收穫。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">取走</span>這個工具組加入你的收藏，或是與目前工具組<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交換</span>。在星球上時，利用快捷選單 (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>) 中的機能選項切換使用中的工具組。"
  },
